    <!-- 解释 -->
<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <dl><dd><ol><li><p> [spiral]∶沿着螺旋轨道运动;旋绕飞行</p><p>飞机在头顶上盘旋</p></li><li><p> [circle]∶指大致呈圆形地运动,也可指迂回绕圈儿</p><p>一群黑鹭在头上高高盘旋,凭着上升的气流不停地兜着圈儿</p></li><li><p> [stay;stop;pace up and down]∶逗留,徘徊</p><p>他在湖天盘旋了很久,舍不得离开</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
